chigurida kanasu ( kannada : ಚಿಗುರಿದ ಕನಸು ) is a 2003 indian kannada film directed by t. s. nagabharana , starring shiva rajkumar , rekha unnikrishnan and avinash in pivotal roles . it is based on a novel of the same name by shivaram karanth , a jnanpith award winner . 2004 hindi movie swades was reported to be inspired by this movie .